Document: RDShaderSource
Path: godot/classes/class_rdshadersource.rst
Summary: Represents a compiled shader source code for the rendering device.

Inherits: Resource < RefCounted

This class represents a compiled shader source code for the rendering device. It holds the shader code in a format that can be directly used by the rendering hardware. This is typically generated by the shader compiler and is not meant to be edited directly by the user. It's a low-level resource used internally by Godot's rendering system.
